{"record_id":"xiaocai:quality_acceptance:unified_quality_acceptance_target","source_id":"domain_seed:xiaocai:quality_acceptance:unified_quality_acceptance_target","title":"验收标准与质量口径统一目标","content":"xiaocai 在需求梳理中应把“质量标准”和“验收口径”对用户展示为一个统一目标：验收标准与质量口径。该目标包括交付物清单、规格/性能指标、安装调试或试运行要求、质保售后、验收材料与通过条件。内部仍可保留质量标准、验收口径等字段，但对用户优先呈现同一个待确认目标，避免重复追问或口径冲突。","metadata":{"domain":"xiaocai","tenant_id":"procurement_china","record_type":"quality_acceptance_policy","review_status":"seeded","confidence":0.88,"tags":["质量标准","验收口径","需求梳理目标"],"source_refs":[{"source_id":"public:iso:9001"},{"source_id":"public:cn:government-procurement-regulation"}]}}
{"record_id":"xiaocai:quality_acceptance:system_software_quality_dimensions","source_id":"domain_seed:xiaocai:quality_acceptance:system_software_quality_dimensions","title":"系统/软件类采购质量口径应覆盖可验证维度","content":"系统、软件、平台和智能化服务采购的质量口径应尽量转成可验证维度，例如功能完整性、性能容量、兼容性、可靠性、安全性、可维护性、易用性、迁移/集成要求和运行验收条件。ISO/IEC 25010 可作为质量维度参考，但具体指标应由采购需求和供应商方案共同确认。","metadata":{"domain":"xiaocai","tenant_id":"procurement_china","record_type":"quality_acceptance_policy","review_status":"seeded","confidence":0.78,"tags":["软件质量","系统验收","可验证指标"],"source_refs":[{"source_id":"public:iso:25010"}]}}
{"record_id":"xiaocai:quality_acceptance:materials_and_pass_conditions","source_id":"domain_seed:xiaocai:quality_acceptance:materials_and_pass_conditions","title":"验收材料与通过条件应在需求阶段预埋","content":"需求阶段应尽量预埋验收材料和通过条件，包括到货清单、配置/规格证明、测试报告、安装调试记录、试运行记录、培训记录、质保服务承诺、发票或合同附件要求，以及不通过时的整改和复验机制。这样可以减少采购后期因“质量标准”和“验收口径”分离造成的争议。","metadata":{"domain":"xiaocai","tenant_id":"procurement_china","record_type":"quality_acceptance_policy","review_status":"seeded","confidence":0.83,"tags":["验收材料","通过条件","质保售后"],"source_refs":[{"source_id":"public:cn:government-procurement-law"},{"source_id":"public:cn:government-procurement-regulation"}]}}
